    "abstract": "<jats:title>Abstract</jats:title>\n                <jats:p>We report an experimental infection of American mink with SARS-CoV-2 Omicron variant and show that minks remain virus RNA positive for days, develop clinical signs and histopathological changes, and transmit the virus to uninfected recipients warranting further studies and preparedness.</jats:p>",
